summary: This document is a certification from the Secretary of State of Delaware confirming that 'JEGE, INC.' is duly incorporated and in good standing as of September 23, 2013. It states that annual reports and franchise taxes have been filed and paid to date.
keyFacts: The document certifies that 'JEGE, INC.' is incorporated in Delaware.
The certification confirms that the corporation is in good standing.
Annual reports and franchise taxes for 'JEGE, INC.' have been filed and paid as of the date of the document.
